后中国多达 15 年，因为北京政府支持的技术方法和广泛的融资使其具有优势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 04:04:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/us-many-15-years-behind-china-nuclear-power-report-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>国防部长称台湾不寻求与中国开战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-is-not-seeking-war-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-17/</link><description>台湾国防部长顾维钧周一表示，台湾并不寻求与北京开战，其政策是建立防御性、多层次的威慑能力，使中国更难占领该岛。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 03:11:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-is-not-seeking-war-with-china-defence-minister-says-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国工厂产出令人失望，房地产业陷入低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-may-industrial-output-misses-forecasts-retail-sales-bright-spot-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国5月份工业产出低于预期，尽管有政策支持，但房地产行业的放缓并未显示出缓解的迹象，这加大了北京提振经济增长的压力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:24:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-may-industrial-output-misses-forecasts-retail-sales-bright-spot-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国新房价格跌幅创近10年来最快</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-clip-nearly-10-years-2024-06-17/</link><description>周一官方数据显示，5月份中国新房价格跌幅为逾9-1/2年来最快，尽管政府努力遏制供应过剩并支持负债累累的开发商，但房地产行业仍在努力寻找底部。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:05:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-new-home-prices-fall-fastest-clip-nearly-10-years-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>1-5月中国房地产投资下滑加剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-investment-slump-worsens-january-may-2024-06-17/</link><description>尽管政策制定者加倍努力支持陷入困境的行业和提振消费者信心，但中国的房地产投资在 1 月至 4 月下降 9.8% 后，2024 年前 5 个月仍同比下降 10.1%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 02:04:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-property-investment-slump-worsens-january-may-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国央行维持关键政策利率不变符合预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-06-17/</link><description>中国央行周一在到期中期贷款展期时，如预期维持关键政策利率不变，并从银行体系抽走部分资金。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 01:28:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/china-cbank-leaves-key-policy-rate-unchanged-expected-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>美元企稳，货币盘整，欧元徘徊在一个月低点附近</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-euro-wallows-near-recent-lows-market-braces-china-data-2024-06-17/</link><description>美元周一坚挺，因欧洲政治动荡，欧元徘徊在一个多月低点附近，而投资者则等待有关美国经济实力的新线索。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 01:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-firm-euro-wallows-near-recent-lows-market-braces-china-data-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国消费者需求疲软和中国数据导致油价下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-inch-down-weaker-us-consumer-demand-ahead-china-data-2024-06-17/</link><description>周五的调查显示美国消费者需求疲软，且全球最大原油进口国中国 5 月份原油产量增加，周一亚洲交易时段油价下跌。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 00:59:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-inch-down-weaker-us-consumer-demand-ahead-china-data-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国数据令亚洲股市低迷，欧元处于守势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-17/</link><description>亚洲股市周一下跌，因中国经济消息喜忧参半，突显该国复苏之路坎坷，而欧洲政治不确定性削弱了风险偏好，令欧元处于守势。</description><pubDate>Mon, 17 Jun 2024 00:43:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-06-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国海警称菲律宾补给船在南海与中国船只发生碰撞</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-philippine-supply-ship-illegally-intruded-waters-second-2024-06-16/</link><description>中国海警周一表示，一艘菲律宾补给船在非法侵入南海仁爱礁附近海域后，危险地接近一艘中国船只，导致轻微碰撞。马尼拉军方称这一说法“具有欺骗性和欺骗性”。误导”。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:33:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-coast-guard-says-philippine-supply-ship-illegally-intruded-waters-second-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>中国投资者热衷海外资产刺激财富流入香港</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-offshore-assets-spurs-hong-kong-wealth-inflows-2024-06-16/</link><description>自中国放宽“财富通”计划的投资规则以来，这一趋势一直在加速。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-investors-rush-offshore-assets-spurs-hong-kong-wealth-inflows-2024-06-16/</guid></item><item><title>由于成本、签证障碍，中国出境游复苏滞后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-outbound-travel-recovery-lags-due-costs-visa-snags-2024-06-16/</link><description>复苏的延迟正在打击与旅游相关的公司、酒店和零售商。</description><pubDate>Sun, 16 Jun 2024 23:02:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-outbound-travel-recovery-lags-due-costs-visa-snags-2024-06-16/</guid></item></channel></rss>